'''Hangar 13'''是[[2K_Games|2K Games]]于2014年12月在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[诺瓦托_(加利福尼亚州)|诺瓦托]]前{{le|汉密尔顿空军基地|Hamilton Army Airfield}}成立的游戏开发工作室，由漫画书和电子游戏作者{{le|哈登·布莱克曼|Haden Blackman}}主管。2016年10月7日，工作室处女作《[[黑手党3|黑手党3]]》面世。

== 简史 ==

2014年12月4日，[[2K_Games|2K Games]]宣布成立新游戏工作室Hangar 13，由行业老将、前[[LucasArts|LucasArts]][[创意总监|创意总监]]{{le|哈登·布莱克曼|Haden Blackman}}领军<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/12/4/7331207/2k-games-hangar-13-new-studio-haden-blackman|title=2K Games forms new studio led by ex-LucasArts creative director Haden Blackman|first=Michael|last=McWhertor|work=Polygon|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424020625/http://www.polygon.com/2014/12/4/7331207/2k-games-hangar-13-new-studio-haden-blackman|dead-url=no}}</ref>。布莱克曼告诉GamesBeat，工作室将创作[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[个人电脑|PC]]平台游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2014/12/04/2k-launches-brand-new-next-generation-console-game-studio-hangar-13/|title=2K launches brand new console game studio Hangar 13|first=Dean|last=Takahashi|work=VentureBeat|date=2012-12-04|accessdate=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160226142730/http://venturebeat.com/2014/12/04/2k-launches-brand-new-next-generation-console-game-studio-hangar-13/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

处女作《[[黑手党3|黑手党3]]》于2015年7月28日公布先导预告，并于2015年8月5日在[[Gamescom|Gamescom 2015]]正式公布剧场版预告<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2015/08/05/mafia-3-reveal-trailer-gamescom-2015/|title=Mafia 3: here’s the reveal trailer as promised|first=Stephany|last=Nunneley|work=VG247|date=2015-08-05|accessdate=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528184257/https://www.vg247.com/2015/08/05/mafia-3-reveal-trailer-gamescom-2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2K_Czech|2K Czech]]配合游戏开发<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2015/10/14/who-the-hell-is-mafia-iiis-hangar-13.aspx|title=Who The Hell Is Mafia III Developer Hangar 13?|first=Ben|last=Hanson|work=Game Informer|date=2015-10-14|accessdate=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517003401/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2015/10/14/who-the-hell-is-mafia-iiis-hangar-13.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏于2016年10月7日登陆[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/mafia-3-release-date-announced-new-trailer-and-del/1100-6438967/|title=Mafia 3 Release Date Announced, New Trailer and Deluxe Versions Revealed|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|work=GameSpot|date=2016-04-19|accessdate=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504072441/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/mafia-3-release-date-announced-new-trailer-and-del/1100-6438967/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，2K宣布将[[2K_Czech|2K Czech]]并入到Hangar 13中。

2020年5月，2K宣布将发售《黑手党三部曲》的高清重制版，包括了《[[黑手党：失落天堂|黑手党：失落天堂]]》的完全高清重制版、《[[黑手党2|黑手党2]]》的高清复刻版游戏以及包含追加下载内容的《[[黑手党3|黑手党3]]》完全版。《黑手党：失落天堂》的完全重制和《黑手党2》的高清化将由Hangar 13负责制作。<ref>[https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/363242/2K_and_Hangar_13_get_in_on_the_classic_game_remake_trend_with_Mafia_Definitive_Edition.php 2K and Hangar 13 get in on the classic game remake trend with Mafia: Definitive Edition] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/363242/2K_and_Hangar_13_get_in_on_the_classic_game_remake_trend_with_Mafia_Definitive_Edition.php |date=20200614031635 }}.Gamasutra.2020-05-19.[2020-06-14].</ref><ref>[https://www.gamesradar.com/mafia-trilogy-launches-today-with-a-mafia-remake-releasing-in-august/ Mafia: Trilogy launches today, with a Mafia remake releasing in August] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/mafia-trilogy-launches-today-with-a-mafia-remake-releasing-in-august/ |date=20200614031633 }}.Gameradar.2020-05-19.[2020-06-14].</ref>

